# Virtual Assistant

Virtual Assistant is a webpage that looks to match virtual assistants from latin america to Companies all around the world.



## Usage

You can create an account either as a company hiring or someone looking for a job.

It has an integrated chat wich can be only started by companies

The status of each application of an offer can be updated by the company who posted the offer, and after it is approved for an interview the calendar will automatically display showing available dates for it.

